Feature: Batch Operations


Scenario: Recursive status change on assembly
    GIVEN an assembly with multiple occurrences exists
    WHEN a batch recursive status change on the assembly is run
    THEN the status has been changed on the complete structure


Scenario: Non Recursive status change on assembly
    GIVEN an assembly with multiple occurrences exists
    WHEN a batch status change on the assembly is run
    THEN the status has not been changed on the assembly
